channel.title: 194 Beta help
channel.description:
hey guys, im completely new to all of this rs hacking stuff.
i recently found a thread with the 194 files and i was wondering how to open it. im not interested in making an internet server, just for myself to see how 194 looked. i got to the point where you put in your login but it says
"no response from server please try a different world"
i know that i am nowhere near my goal but can you guys help? thx

item.title: 194 Beta help
item.dc:creator: @Sanskrit Sanskrit
item.description:
@Sanskrit wrote:

So far I have only seen 317 server engines loading a 194 “look-alike” client. I haven’ t been able to find a legitimate server running completely off of 194 protocol.

So yes, you or somebody else will have to write a server to work with that specific client.

Read full topic
